le=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #726c7a;\">Future plans:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',sans-serif; color: #726c7a;\">The main goal is to work for the development of children with disabilities and take initiative and implement it properly so that the children with special needs get vocational education along with academic education so that these children can function as normal people in society and become independent. Above all, through proper planning, establish Dhanaidaha Haque Autistic &amp; Buddhi Protibondhi Biddaloy as the best and exemplary institution in the world, so that other schools can follow or imitate the institution.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/', 'https://www.linkedin.com/', 1),
